title: The Tribe of Hipparchus
info:
Tune 6 of a serie about the Moon.

First composed on DigiBooster (Amiga)
Some improvments with MadTracker (PC)

List of "The Moon" tunes:

01 - Launching of Starship to the Moon
02 - Around the Moon
03 - Lunaport
04 - On Mare Nubium
05 - Moon Dancer
06 - The Tribe of Hipparchus
07 - The Breath of Montes Haemus
08 - Goodbye Moon

Hope you will enjoy the trip !
